---
title: Grilled Smash Beef Burgers with Grilled Onions and Creamy Pickle Slaw
description: There really isn't anything like a perfectly grilled burger topped with grilled onions, cheddar cheese and pickles for a summer meal! Paired with a zippy pickle slaw, this dinner is patio perfection!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/smashed-burgers-de-boeuf-grilles-d271775a.jpg
